---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const phone = '(352) 292-1499';
const phoneTel = '3522921499';
const city = 'Land O\' Lakes';
const county = 'Pasco County';
---

<Layout 
  title={`Concrete Contractors in ${city}, FL | Driveways, Patios & Slabs`}
  description={`Quality concrete contractors in ${city}, Florida. Expert driveways, patios, and slabs for one of Tampa Bay's fastest-growing communities. Call ${phone}!`}
  canonical="/locations/land-o-lakes/"
>
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Concrete Contractors in {city}, Florida</h1>
      <p>Professional concrete services for {city}'s growing community. Quality driveways, patios, and slabs.</p>
      <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {phone}</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h2>Concrete Services for {city}</h2>
          <p>{city} has transformed from a quiet agricultural community into one of Tampa Bay's most desirable addresses. New master-planned communities sit alongside established neighborhoods, creating a mix of concrete needs—from brand-new construction to updates for older properties.</p>
          
          <p>Brooksville Concrete Co. serves Land O' Lakes and surrounding areas of southern Pasco County. While our home base is in Hernando County, Land O' Lakes is well within our service area, and we've helped numerous homeowners throughout the community improve their properties with quality concrete work.</p>
          
          <p>Whether you're in one of the newer developments like Connerton or Starkey Ranch, or in an established Land O' Lakes neighborhood, we deliver concrete that meets your needs and exceeds your expectations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h3>{city} Concrete Services</h3>
          <ul class="why-list">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Residential Driveways</strong>
                Driveways that complement Land O' Lakes homes, from simple to decorative.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Patios & Outdoor Living</strong>
                Extend your living space outdoors with a beautiful concrete patio.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Pool Decks</strong>
                Safe, attractive pool surrounds with slip-resistant finishes.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Slabs & Additions</strong>
                Foundations for workshops, garages, and home additions.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-content">
    <h2>Quality Concrete for Growing Communities</h2>
    
    <p>Land O' Lakes' rapid growth means many homeowners are looking to personalize newer homes or update aging properties. Concrete improvements—new patios, extended driveways, pool decks—are popular upgrades that enhance both enjoyment and property value.</p>

    <h3>Working in HOA Communities</h3>
    
    <p>Many Land O' Lakes neighborhoods have homeowner associations with specific guidelines for exterior improvements. We're experienced in working within these requirements, ensuring your concrete project meets all applicable standards while delivering the results you want.</p>
    
    <p>Before starting any Land O' Lakes project, we can help you understand what approvals may be needed and work with you through the process. Our professional appearance and clean work habits help projects go smoothly in community settings.</p>

    <h3>Premium Materials and Techniques</h3>
    
    <p>Every Land O' Lakes project uses our standard premium specifications:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li>4,000+ PSI concrete for superior strength</li>
      <li>Fiber reinforcement to prevent cracking</li>
      <li>Proper joint placement for expansion control</li>
      <li>Quality sealers for long-lasting appearance</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>These materials and techniques ensure your concrete looks great and performs well in Florida's demanding climate.</p>

    <h3>Decorative Options</h3>
    
    <p>Land O' Lakes homeowners often want concrete that makes a statement. Our decorative options include stamped concrete in patterns mimicking stone, brick, or tile; colored concrete that coordinates with your home's exterior; exposed aggregate for texture and visual interest; and various finishing techniques for unique looks.</p>

    <h3>Schedule Your Consultation</h3>
    
    <p>Ready to improve your Land O' Lakes property with quality concrete? Contact Brooksville Concrete Co. for a free estimate. Call <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`}>{phone}</a> or submit our online form.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Professional Concrete for {city}</h2>
      <p>Quality work for Tampa Bay's growing communities</p>
      <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`} class="btn">Call {phone} Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
